com.autonomy.aci.client.transport.gss

Class GssAciServerDetails

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.autonomy.aci.client.transport.AciServerDetails
      • com.autonomy.aci.client.transport.gss.GssAciServerDetails
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class GssAciServerDetails
extends AciServerDetails
    Holds connection details about an ACI Server that is secured using GSS-API. It is a subclass of AciServerDetails that has the addition of the service name of the ACI server to be contacted.
